snippet.title: Starri's New Game Scene First Look: Explore the Cosmos ✨🪐
snippet.description:
A first look at our work in progress game scene: Take a thrilling flight through the ever changing cosmos as you move to the beat. Stay tuned for our upcoming Steam release to experience the epic journey through space (and more)!
➡️ Wishlist Starri on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1940410/Starri/
